{"tid":1803583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"30/12/2019 鏗鏘集--  WE CONNECT","createTime":"2019-12-30T10:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T11:16:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0d709a50176efd144ef1fe1a95ac40e93c57fe","tid":1803583,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"多年以來，政府一直推動社會共融，不過港人和少數族裔依然有隔膜。十月中，九龍大遊行前夕，民陣召集人遇襲。即時新聞指，行兇者懷疑是南亞裔人士，網上討論區上隨即有人建議去衝擊少數族裔聚居的重慶大廈，向南亞人報復，令整個社群人心惶惶。於香港土生土長的少數族裔社群領袖JEFFREY和KK決定要扭轉局勢，結果喜出望外，他們形容是港人與他們「we connect」的新一頁，開始接納他們也是香港人的身份。"},{"pid":"29fd84e10b2a7feaeb38f9e57b533e0607a496e1","tid":1803583,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=49ddfe82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=f5f7287d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要35000人 </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803447\" data-au